>\n<br />\n不過無咩特別返工都係打英文多架啦<br />\n除非中資"},{"pid":"2386cf85476a08bd121eaf35ec11b97a56610f8a","tid":101643,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"手寫板"},{"pid":"624dc8d0f09c0843d52f5896f8a6e9ffea27b7c7","tid":101643,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"而家呢個年代無晒icq玩電話<br />\n唔再識速成倉頡？"},{"pid":"0df60f02960760d84ec6ace9db5712e217268f05","tid":101643,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"返咩工要打中文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e255531f60a885b8cd03a11562eb7556dc2e3a3","tid":101643,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家呢個年代無晒icq玩電話<br />\n唔再識速成倉頡？</blockquote><br />\n我係當年買iPhone<br />\n未有速成 又懶手寫<br />\n結果就學識咗倉頡"},{"pid":"62a2970407c372f837e276b745b0b4e16d12ff35","tid":101643,"uid":28054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返咩工要打中文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同同事im 都要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5895124403ecc4e91fc9db6bd7f7c27a3a62ab7f","tid":101643,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返咩工要打中文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同同事im 都要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同同事都係用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee3b098d19e755037a10bf2a47e5c3e0242054d","tid":101643,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"唔使打中文"}]}